Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.47,0:01:03.91,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot more people around town have \Nbeen wearing yellow recently, haven’t they?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.91,0:01:04.82,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,The Yellow Scarves?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.82,0:01:05.83,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.83,0:01:08.21,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a rumor that the Slasher is part of the Dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.21,0:01:10.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We really do need you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.70,0:01:12.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How's your boyfriend been?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.16,0:01:14.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He comes to visit sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.08,0:01:15.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At least until recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.08,0:01:18.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think the air in Tokyo is dirty?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.71,0:01:22.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Parasite! Parasite! Parasite!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.95,0:01:52.66,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.66,0:01:56.75,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Some Raira Academy students just got assaulted by the Slasher!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.75,0:01:58.72,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.72,0:02:00.54,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,How dangerous...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.54,0:02:02.59,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,As serious as the stare of Daimajin!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.59,0:02:05.10,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard they were first year girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.10,0:02:06.09,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.09,0:02:08.77,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to make a call, so I'm going to lurk for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.77,0:02:09.85,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.29,0:02:12.23,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently it wasn't your girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.80,0:02:14.92,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.92,0:02:17.02,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm still kind of worried about her...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.02,0:02:18.31,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.31,0:02:20.11,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know where it happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.11,0:02:21.38,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.38,0:02:25.27,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not far from the Eastern Ikebukuro subway station that borders the Shuto Expressway.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.27,0:02:30.56,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,But there are a lot of police cruisers\N there, so it should be easy to find.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.56,0:02:31.67,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.56,0:02:34.92,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'm leaving for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.92,0:02:37.42,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Setton, you going rubbernecking?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.97,0:02:38.67,ASS Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(235,115)}Setton has left the chat room.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.67,0:02:40.18,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, c'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.18,0:02:41.47,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.47,0:02:42.68,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.68,0:02:43.51,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.51,0:02:44.92,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get through to her?
