Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.69,0:03:37.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.49,0:03:47.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.86,0:03:51.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A welcome-home greeting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.27,0:03:56.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home, Celty!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.85,0:04:02.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.99,0:04:08.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:10.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just saw something horrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.53,0:04:15.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Something horrifying?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.68,0:04:19.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me say it! I want to forget!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:20.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.86,0:04:24.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you at least take that white thing off when you shower?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.40,0:04:29.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope. The air here in Tokyo is dirty,\N so I can't just take it off whenever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.33,0:04:32.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, That's right.\N Good job last night, Celty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.17,0:04:37.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And just who were those brutes wearing all that yellow?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.17,0:04:39.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They're the Yellow Scarves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.49,0:04:43.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They appeared around the time you left for America.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.37,0:04:47.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They got in a brawl with the Blue Squares a\N while ago and were supposed to have calmed down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.88,0:04:52.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph. They should just destroy each other and go die in some sewer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.72,0:04:54.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.58,0:05:00.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Celty brought you here safely, so pay the fee.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.84,0:05:02.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Put it on my tab.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.14,0:05:03.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.78,0:05:07.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll just bilk you out of it like I always do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.90,0:05:12.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just testing you, Celty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.18,0:05:15.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you just let me go now—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.03,0:05:16.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.39,0:05:17.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cutting into me! It's cutting into me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.51,0:05:19.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,These shadow thorns are cutting into me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.81,0:05:24.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinra! My life is in real danger here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.91,0:05:27.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What should you do in this kind of situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.41,0:05:29.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd know if you were my son!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.71,0:05:31.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.60,0:05:34.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.10,0:05:38.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:42.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not giving you an inheritance, so that can be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.94,0:05:45.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need any.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.93,0:05:48.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been had by a monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.07,0:05:53.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd truly been had, she would've taken your soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.49,0:05:56.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:05:59.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, well, Celty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.22,0:06:03.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you...in love with Shinra?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.80,0:06:11.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew my son would be weird enough to get \Nattached to you, but do you actually like him too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.55,0:06:14.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.35,0:06:15.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Celty!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.85,0:06:19.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's great that you're being so honest about our relationship!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.54,0:06:23.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that our connection, which I \Nthought was no more than unrequited love,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.76,0:06:29.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,has developed into a solid relationship\N that we can boldly express in front of others...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:31.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fills me with thoughts of jumping for joy—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.99,0:06:34.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it; you're embarrassing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.29,0:06:43.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think I'd approve of this relationship?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.07,0:06:43.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.92,0:06:48.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an uninvited guest in human society.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.20,0:06:52.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're aware of the fact that you're\N commonly referred to as a monster, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.00,0:06:53.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.07,0:06:55.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Of course," she says...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.09,0:06:58.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So what? Do you have a problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.04,0:07:04.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems my plan to point out that she \Nwon't fit into society has failed miserably.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.37,0:07:07.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not in the least bit convincing, coming from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.73,0:07:09.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.84,0:07:14.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinra says he likes me the way I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.68,0:07:16.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph. There's nothing I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.60,0:07:18.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I approve of you two dating.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.89,0:07:22.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In return, you shall call me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.27,0:07:24.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...my beloved father!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.97,0:07:25.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shove it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.78,0:07:29.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, Celty...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.98,0:07:32.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your memories will never return as long as you remain headless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.41,0:07:39.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your memories of when you were a dullahan in your native country of Ireland, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.06,0:07:40.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.38,0:07:41.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Something I'll have to live with.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.56,0:07:48.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's create a lot of memories \Ntogether to make up for the ones you've lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.03,0:07:51.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinra...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.72,0:07:54.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For starters, let's hold a wedding!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.29,0:08:00.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll measure your for your wedding dress,\N so take off those shadow clothes—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.68,0:08:06.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, you were a perverted \Nchild who'd laugh merrily at an autopsy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.33,0:08:08.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He definitely gets that from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.64,0:08:10.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not "you," it's "my beloved father!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.96,0:08:18.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly...I just said it a moment ago.\N You're as thoughtless as ever, Celty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.31,0:08:21.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you had no idea I stole your head—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.98,0:08:22.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.50,0:08:27.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.06,0:08:29.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-Wh-What did you just say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.81,0:08:33.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do? I just spilled the beans about an important secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.94,0:08:35.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.17,0:08:38.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Celty's an airhead, so she won't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.29,0:08:38.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.83,0:08:42.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Celty the airhead, Celty the airhead...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.53,0:08:43.33,Secondary,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Why'd you say that twice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.68,0:08:48.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because the attacks of a frenzied airhead are easy to rea—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.08,0:08:52.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you make fun of Celty, even if you are my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.50,0:08:55.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it, I get it! I'll explain everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.94,0:08:58.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there's no point in hiding it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.20,0:09:04.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The person who stole your head and sold it to a \Npharmaceutical company was none other than me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.24,0:09:05.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be such a jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.46,0:09:06.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.69,0:09:07.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.92,0:09:09.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I want to show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.86,0:09:23.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? He ran away?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.43,0:09:28.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That perverted freak...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.64,0:09:29.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.95,0:09:40.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.14,0:09:47.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems my "just push the elevator button" plan was a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.88,0:09:49.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to get my bags.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.76,0:09:50.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:51.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Beep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.65,0:10:01.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, where'd he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.21,0:10:08.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Celty...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.19,0:10:10.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.70,0:10:12.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just spacing out in a place like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:15.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm thinking about some stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.90,0:10:17.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.35,0:10:21.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,About that "stuff." You look pretty depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:26.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about the Slasher...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.01,0:10:29.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are some weird rumors on the Net and message boards...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.62,0:10:31.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Weird rumors?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.22,0:10:35.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, like the Slasher is part of the Dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.29,0:10:36.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.66,0:10:38.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.82,0:10:41.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I don't, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.55,0:10:47.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But something dangerous will probably happen if the rumor gets around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:52.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially since relations between the Dollars and \Nthe Yellow Scarves are strained enough as they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.05,0:10:59.30,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,The balance of this city certainly is hanging over a precipice...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.93,0:11:02.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikado...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.52,0:11:05.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll look into the Slasher incidents as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.41,0:11:06.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Celty...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.21,0:11:09.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.07,0:11:14.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're bound to get caught up in \Nsomething just zoning out in this type of place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.51,0:11:16.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.90,0:11:18.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.28,0:11:23.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Slasher, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.07,0:11:26.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but it doesn't ring a bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.43,0:11:27.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.21,0:11:33.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason for you to do all this for the Dollars, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.21,0:11:35.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just for the Dollars...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.82,0:11:39.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a history with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.44,0:11:45.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I weren't headless, I'd be dead now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.90,0:11:47.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.97,0:11:52.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,People who call others idiots are usually more idiotic, but I'm an idiot, so I'll say it anyway:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.76,0:11:55.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! You should've said something!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.09,0:11:56.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, I'm gonna kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.35,0:11:57.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll definitely kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.34,0:11:58.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Without a doubt, I'll kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.75,0:12:00.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hunt him down and kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.46,0:12:03.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I'm the headless rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.72,0:12:05.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:06.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.50,0:12:08.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no longer just about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.90,0:12:12.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Drawing your sword usually means certain death, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.12,0:12:16.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill him...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.61,0:12:15.02,Secondary,,0000,0000,0000,,What about your work?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.02,0:12:16.25,Secondary,,0000,0000,0000,,You're only on break now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.25,0:12:17.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.94,0:12:22.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now, I'm not going to let you get fired over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.46,0:12:27.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover, I need a lot more information before I search for the Slasher.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.05,0:12:30.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you at least wait until I'm done with all my preparations?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.76,0:12:34.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.77,0:12:37.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But make it as fast as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.64,0:12:41.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill him...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.05,0:12:46.45,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a reason I parted with Shizuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.65,0:12:54.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, I'm so happy you came to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.96,0:12:56.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, how are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.72,0:12:58.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.41,0:13:00.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.43,0:13:02.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get right to the point:
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.53,0:13:04.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know about the Slasher.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.96,0:13:06.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Three bills should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.12,0:13:15.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Although, your clothes and your wallet are made of shadows, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.74,0:13:21.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it's possible to shine a light on \Nthem that's bright enough to leave you naked.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.23,0:13:22.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to see me naked?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.85,0:13:24.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.44,0:13:28.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike a certain perverted,\N black-market medical scholar,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.83,0:13:32.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't lust after headless or bodiless girl—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.54,0:13:36.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.23,0:13:39.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I won't let you off so easily the next time you insult Shinra.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.77,0:13:42.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You two sure do love each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.12,0:13:46.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.13,0:13:52.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What would happen if another dullahan came along, seduced him, and stole his heart...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.78,0:13:55.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to think that wouldn't happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.26,0:13:56.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But if it does, it does...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.46,0:13:58.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you kill Shinra yourself then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.65,0:14:00.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.09,0:14:02.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wouldn't let him go near...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.01,0:14:04.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Another headless woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.26,0:14:08.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I love him, too, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.80,0:14:13.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's surprising!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.68,0:14:16.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've become even more human!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.93,0:14:19.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.33,0:14:21.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The closer you get to becoming human...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.53,0:14:26.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The bigger the gap will be when you get your head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.35,0:14:29.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll think about that after I actually get my head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.22,0:14:35.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, to be honest, I've been thinking that I might not even need my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.04,0:14:38.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, give me that information about the Slasher.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.91,0:14:41.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you don't know anything after you've taken my money.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.61,0:14:44.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.18,0:14:48.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have some special information that I've yet to leak to the police, the media, or the Net.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.56,0:14:51.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I've been waiting for you to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.34,0:14:52.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.87,0:14:57.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This incident belongs in the realm of the fantastical.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.03,0:15:00.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know of a katana called Saika?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.76,0:15:01.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Saika...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.78,0:15:07.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It may be hard to believe, but Saika is an \Nethereal sword that used to reside in Shinjuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.62,0:15:09.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,An ethereal sword...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.02,0:15:11.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the Muramasa Blade?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.12,0:15:12.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.17,0:15:14.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a katana with dubious magical powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.97,0:15:18.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.61,0:15:22.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard about some ethereal sword called Saika from Izaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.60,0:15:28.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a legend that it has a mind of its own and takes control of humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.66,0:15:35.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, every single one of the Slasher's victims says that it has red eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.67,0:15:38.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying that's because of the Saika?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.36,0:15:39.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.58,0:15:45.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The night the Slasher first appeared, someone with the handle "Saika" logged onto the network I use.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.87,0:15:52.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But when I was attacked, I didn't notice it approaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.78,0:15:57.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I should be able to sense something if Saika isn't human.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.97,0:16:03.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be because the Saika can only control one's mind, while the person's body is the thing that's actually moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.92,0:16:08.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's understandable why you couldn't sense any type of presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.27,0:16:11.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinra, you seem pretty knowledgeable about Saika...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.78,0:16:15.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you told me to look into it before, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.85,0:16:18.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, come to bed quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.54,0:16:26.29,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1320)}I thought, "Shinra's hiding something."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.03,0:16:38.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.18,0:16:48.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When I conducted my own search for Miss Namie after Nebula merged with Yagiri Pharmaceuticals, I found out that she frequents your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.18,0:16:53.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So I threatened her with this model gun and she let me come in with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.00,0:16:54.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A model gun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.33,0:16:56.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I didn't tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.56,0:17:00.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't we report this guy to the police?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.24,0:17:04.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, won't you be the ones in trouble if you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.68,0:17:10.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Once the police conduct a search of this room based on \Nmy testimony, they'll find the head of some young woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.59,0:17:11.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.73,0:17:15.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This might become a first-rate scandal to take the place of the Slasher.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.56,0:17:20.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So...Shinra does get his twisted personality from you after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.24,0:17:22.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get anything for complimenting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.46,0:17:27.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, to be honest, I'm in no rush to get the head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.63,0:17:28.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.74,0:17:35.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The executives at my company are quite \Nsurprised at what they saw of Celty on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.39,0:17:40.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They've decided that her body should be studied before her head.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.05,0:17:46.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I've unilaterally decided that the \Nlocation of her head is "currently under investigation."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.16,0:17:52.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, it seems that you've taken quite \Nan interesting approach concerning her head.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.00,0:18:00.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Based on the theory that a valkyrie is a dullahan, you try to awaken it by causing a power struggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.18,0:18:03.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What a unique idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.36,0:18:06.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm testing it in various ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.06,0:18:10.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If worse comes to worst, I might just have to bring it to a war zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.84,0:18:15.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'd be happy to cooperate with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.05,0:18:17.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.15,0:18:19.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also interested in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.60,0:18:26.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't many people around who'd conduct\N research from a mythological point of view, including myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.69,0:18:28.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.24,0:18:32.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well now, why don't I give you a piece of advice?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.63,0:18:40.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do cause some manufactured conflict in order to stimulate either Celty's head or spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.74,0:18:44.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,don't involve her in some clash of wills between other people...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.04,0:18:46.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But make her body the center of it all...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.58,0:18:51.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And throw those around her into the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.16,0:18:56.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I plan on doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.98,0:19:01.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Things are being set in motion faster than I'd anticipated.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.83,0:19:05.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anri...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.95,0:19:07.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're already making preparations for the sports festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.95,0:19:09.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you're okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.87,0:19:10.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.70,0:19:12.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.54,0:19:15.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why were you with those students who got slashed?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.91,0:19:18.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't being bullied again, were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.90,0:19:20.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.16,0:19:22.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I really am.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.13,0:19:25.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Slasher might come after you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.28,0:19:26.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous to go out alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.86,0:19:28.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sexually harassing her again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.76,0:19:31.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't have that now, can we?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.77,0:19:33.80,Secondary,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just worried about Anri.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.80,0:19:35.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, using only her first name?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.36,0:19:36.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.73,0:19:43.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you worry too much, Anri might transfer out like Niekawa did.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.69,0:19:49.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You were Niekawa Haruna's homeroom teacher last year, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.93,0:19:50.96,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.36,0:19:53.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You know about Niekawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.26,0:19:55.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, in name only.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.54,0:19:58.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,On that note, us students have to go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.01,0:20:03.78,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Who in the world is Niekawa Haruna...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.78,0:20:06.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Anri...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.01,0:20:09.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikado hasn't confessed to you yet, has he?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.92,0:20:10.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.54,0:20:12.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.02,0:20:15.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But you have noticed he's totally fallen for you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.86,0:20:20.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryugamine's a good friend, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.73,0:20:27.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My best friend seems like he truly does \Nlove you, so I'm going to look after you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.03,0:20:31.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, I should get along well with beautiful girls from all over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.46,0:20:32.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Masaomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.11,0:20:35.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sonohara!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.08,0:20:38.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Enter the coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.09,0:20:39.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.86,0:20:42.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd turn into a fossil waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.26,0:20:42.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.95,0:20:43.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Square root of three points.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.95,0:20:46.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A square root? What's a square root?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.10,0:20:49.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At least make your criticism easy to understand with something like "minus twenty points."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.42,0:20:50.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.42,0:20:51.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.93,0:20:53.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.66,0:21:13.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You finally came.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.53,0:21:27.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Celty...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.45,0:21:30.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,About Saika...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.67,0:21:34.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was in my father's possession for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.43,0:21:38.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He apparently sold it to an antique shop a few years ago, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.50,0:21:39.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shingen had it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.95,0:21:40.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.98,0:21:44.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's said... that the Saika can cut people's souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.06,0:21:47.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.27,0:21:48.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.78,0:21:52.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He used the Saika to steal your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.51,0:21:55.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He used it to cut the soul that bound your head and body together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.85,0:22:01.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And you knew about that, Shinra...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.01,0:22:02.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.13,0:22:06.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I realized he used it to steal your head only \Nafter I'd conducted my own investigation after the fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.37,0:22:12.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd best not say anything, since you were trying to forget about your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.40,0:22:13.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.64,0:22:15.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.84,0:22:18.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me think about this on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.71,0:22:24.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.30,0:22:27.74,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Love breeds confusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.74,0:22:32.86,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,That same night, the ethereal sword Saika was trying to find a certain girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.86,0:22:37.37,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,A girl who couldn't find her own place in this reality...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.69,0:22:39.99,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Sonohara Anri.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.32,0:24:16.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ikebukuro:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.93,0:24:19.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All I wanted was to learn about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.62,0:24:23.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,About the source of this refuse-packed city's energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.32,0:24:26.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and the truth behind this city that bulges with desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.56,0:24:29.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Time: Even Fools Can Give Good Counsel.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.07,0:24:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
